---
// src/components/Products.astro
---

<section id="produk" class="products-section">
    <div class="section-title">
        <h2>Perangkat Keras MATAPADI</h2>
        <p>Sistem *smart farming* tangguh yang dirancang khusus untuk operasional lapangan 24/7 di bawah kondisi cuaca ekstrem.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="product-showcase">
        <div class="product-gallery">
            <figure class="product-card">
                <div class="image-wrapper">
                    <img src="/matapadi-1.jpeg" alt="Sistem MATAPADI Tampak Depan dengan Panel Surya" loading="lazy" />
                </div>
                <figcaption>
                    <h3>Tampak Depan</h3>
                    <p>Modul utama dengan kamera pengawas AI dan corong pengusir ultrasonik.</p>
                </figcaption>
            </figure>

            <figure class="product-card">
                <div class="image-wrapper">
                    <img src="/matapadi-2.jpeg" alt="MATAPADI Tampak Samping dengan Panel Surya" loading="lazy" />
                </div>
                <figcaption>
                    <h3>Sistem Kemandirian Energi</h3>
                    <p>Dilengkapi panel surya 50WP untuk memastikan sistem beroperasi tanpa henti.</p>
                </figcaption>
            </figure>

            <figure class="product-card">
                <div class="image-wrapper">
                    <img src="/matapadi-3.jpeg" alt="MATAPADI Tampak Belakang" loading="lazy" />
                </div>
                <figcaption>
                    <h3>Box Industrial Grade</h3>
                    <p>Box panel tahan cuaca (IP65) melindungi komponen elektronik dari hujan dan panas.</p>
                </figcaption>
            </figure>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .products-section {
        background-color: var(--color-bg-alt);
        border-radius: 40px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        padding: 100px 5%;
        max-width: 1360px; /* Slightly wider for the gallery */
    }

    .product-gallery {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 30px; /* slightly smaller gap for mobile friendly */
        margin-top: 50px;
    }

    .product-card {
        background: var(--color-bg);
        border-radius: var(--radius-md);
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
        transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.165, 0.84, 0.44, 1), box-shadow 0.4s ease;
        border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
    }

    .product-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-10px);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    }

    .image-wrapper {
        aspect-ratio: 4/3;
        overflow: hidden;
        background-color: #e5e7eb; /* placeholder color while loading */
        position: relative;
    }

    /* Important: We fix the image aspect ratio so it doesn't look stretched or broken */
    .image-wrapper img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        object-position: center;
        transition: transform 0.7s ease;
    }

    .product-card:hover .image-wrapper img {
        transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    figcaption {
        padding: 30px;
    }

    figcaption h3 {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        color: var(--color-text-main);
    }

    figcaption p {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: var(--color-text-muted);
        line-height: 1.5;
    }
</style>
